overview: More than an hour of holiday fun with The Aquabats! It's time for some holiday cheer with your favorite band of superheroes, The Aquabats! Gather around the fireplace and join us for a cozy Christmas hangout and a loud, rowdy concert... all in one!
tagline: You’ve seen Rudolph the Red-Nosed Reindeer and Home Alone a gazillion times - it’s time to spice up your holiday viewing traditions with The Aquabats!
title: The Aquabats Kooky Kristmas Party
